{"tid":2084743,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人而家食緊a酸醫暗瘡？","createTime":"2020-06-29T12:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T13:28:34.000Z","uid":91574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5b83b6fe657ac7dd78808d0f566550ab0c7f5535","tid":2084743,"uid":91574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:32:55.000Z","msg":"睇開長沙灣陳<br />\n今日諗住去攞藥 點知話呢排啲藥冇貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我個療程仲未完<br />\n上網search下諗住自己上網買藥<br />\n點知周圍都冇<br />\n唔知係咪因為依家肺炎搞到物流停晒<br />\n啲藥出口唔到去香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家諗住睇住第二個醫生先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日去問mk陳 但出面個姑娘好撚臭串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網search見啲人好似都唔係好肯講睇咗幾錢咁<br />\n點解要搞到啲診金資訊咁神秘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知邊度睇暗瘡平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個月一千-二千都負擔到"},{"pid":"82dc62c8c003bfe08f3906bbeb0d09c4ddb4871e","tid":2084743,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"男人食會禿頭"},{"pid":"4f453b20c233e6bd83a02bd6276e48d4f697b764","tid":2084743,"uid":304032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:36:56.000Z","msg":"方慶生 千五一個月<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UJdXVmV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUJdXVmV.jpg&h=1282e70e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffc4eb51ea307da5e792958b478506c7427d33fc","tid":2084743,"uid":91574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f453b20c233e6bd83a02bd6276e48d4f697b764","tid":2084743,"uid":304032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:36:56.000Z","msg":"方慶生 千五一個月<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UJdXVmV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUJdXVmV.jpg&h